OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for some but
OL,6,Fbecoming increasingly sunny with
OL,7,Fpatchy fair weather cloud. Feeling
OL,8,Fwarmer than on Monday though breezier
OL,9,Ftoo, with the easterly wind turning
OL,10,Fblustery particularly over the
OL,11,FPennines and Lake District.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear and dry overnight,
OL,14,Fperhaps with some cloud developing
OL,15,Fhere and there later in the night.
OL,16,FChilly overnight and remaining
OL,17,Fblustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
